@startuml
actor User
participant "FinanceTrackerAPP" as App
participant "树形视图" as Treeview

User -> App: 点击"删除账目"
activate App
App -> Treeview: 获取选中项
Treeview --> App: 返回选中索引
alt 有选中项
  App -> User: 显示确认对话框
  User --> App: 确认删除
  App -> App: 从entries删除数据
  App -> App: save_data()
  App -> Treeview: update_treeview()
  App -> User: 显示成功消息
else 无选中项
  App -> User: 显示警告消息
end
deactivate App
@enduml